metadata.dc:author: Mondragón Espinoza, J
Ardines Limonchi, P
metadata.dc:description: Purpose of this study was to analyze the behavior of some traditional sealing materials, plus one recently appeared, and test their sealing properties, in order to understand and ascertain the problem of non-hermetical sealing, a problem of clinical significance.
metadata.dc:title: Materiales de sellado provisorio: valoración de hermeticidad.
[Provisional sealing materials: evaluation of leakage].
